high_descs: Move a bit to stand at the foot of the bed.
Pick up the cell phone that's closest to you.
Turn, and carry the cell  phone a few steps to the dresser on your left in front of the window.
Place the cell phone on the front left corner of the dresser, which is opposite the blue book.
Turn right and move back to the foot of the bed.
Pick up the other cell phone from the bed.
Carry the phone to once again face the dresser in front of the window.
Place the phone on the dresser to the right of the one you previously left there.
anns.task_desc: Move two cell phones from the bed to the dresser.

high_descs: Approach the bed in front of you.
Pick up the cell phone from the bed.
Turn to your left and walk to the dresser.
Place the cell phone on the dresser next to the chess board.
Turn around and approach the bed.
Pick up the cell phone on the bed
Turn to your left and walk to the dresser.
Place the cell phone on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Place two cell phones on the dresser.

high_descs: Take a step right to the foot of the bed.
Pick up the closest cell phone.
Turn left and look at the left side of the dresser.
Place the cell phone in front of the chess board.
Turn right and look at the bed again.
Pick up the cell phone on the bed.
Turn left to the dresser again.
Place the cell phone to the right of the other cell phone.
anns.task_desc: Place two cell phones on a dresser.
